a + c * e + a + c + 0 ≤ b + d * e + b + d + e :=
add_le_add (add_le_add (add_le_add (add_le_add h1 (mul_le_mul_of_nonneg_right h2 h3)) h1 ) h2) h3

example {a b c d e : nat} (h1 : a ≤ b) (h2 : c ≤ d) (h3 : 0 ≤ e) :
a + c * e + a + c + 0 ≤ b + d * e + b + d + e :=
by back? [add_le_add, mul_le_mul_of_nonneg_right]

